---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import "../styles/global.css";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import headerImage from "../../public/img/flyer3.jpg";
---

<BaseLayout mainText="Entradas" subText="Good Days vs. Club Doméstico">
  <div
    class="bg-black rounded-lg text-white md:w-8/12 lg:w-6/12 xl:w-4/12 mx-auto shadow-zinc-900 shadow-md"
  >
    <div class="w-full bg-black overflow-hidden rounded-t-lg">
      <Image
        src={headerImage}
        alt={`Flyer de Club Doméstico 3`}
        class="w-full sm:object-cover rounded-tl-lg rounded-tr-lg"
        width="600"
        height="600"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="p-4 text-justify text-lg sm:text-xl">
      <div id="card-header" class="flex justify-between items-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <h2 class="font-bold text-lg lg:text-2xl uppercase">
            Escenario Bar
          </h2>
          <h3 class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-pink-300">C.C. Los Nísperos</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col text-right gap-0">
          <span
            class="font-bold rounded-full text-shadow-md text-xl lg:text-2xl tracking-widest"
          >
            27
          </span>

          <span
            class="text-emerald-300 rounded-full text-shadow-md text-lg lg:text-xl"
          >
            SEP
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p class="mt-4">
        Para adquirir tus entradas de este <span class="font-bold"
          >sábado 27 de septiembre</span
        >, solo debes enviarnos la siguiente información:
        <ul class="py-4 px-6 list-disc">
          <li>Nombre y apellido</li>
          <li>Número de cédula</li>
          <li>Captura del pago (si es el caso)</li>
        </ul>
      </p>
    <div id="card-body">
      <p class="w-full">
        <span class="font-bold text-2xl">Cover: $7 o Bs. 1.400</span>
      </p>
      <div class="my-4 pt-4 text-pink-300 border-t-2 border-white">
        <p class="font-bold mb-2">Datos del pago móvil:</p>
        <div class="flex gap-x-2 items-center">
          <span class="select-none tracking-wide">📞</span> 
          <p>0424<span class="select-none">-</span>4029573</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-x-2 items-center">
          <span class="select-none">🏦</span>
          <p>Banco de Venezuela</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-x-2 items-center">
          <span class="select-none tracking-wide -mt-1">🪪</span>
          <p>26<span class="select-none">.</span>337<span class="select-none">.</span>044</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>
        Una vez realices el pago, tómale una captura y escríbenos por WhatsApp
        al <span class="font-bold">0414-4096757</span> o haz clic en el botón de
        abajo.
      </p>
      <a id="card-button"
        href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=584144096757&text=Hola!%20Ac%C3%A1%20te%20env%C3%ADo%20mi%20comprobante%20de%20pago%20para%20la%20fiesta%20de%20Good%20Days%20vs.%20Club%20Dom%C3%A9stico%0A%0ANombre:%0AC%C3%A9dula:"
        class="block mt-4 py-2 px-2 text-center uppercase font-bold text-lg border-2 lg:border-3 bg-emerald-500 border-emerald-500 text-black rounded-lg hover:bg-black hover:text-emerald-500 transition-all mx-auto"
      >
        Enviar comprobante <br /> por WhatsApp
      </a>

    </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
